<h1>MapLegend</h1>
<p>An interactive, toggleable legend control that wires layer visibility groups to a customizable item template.</p>

<h2 id="overview">// overview</h2>
<p>Place <code>MapLegend</code> as a child of <code>SgbMap</code>. It renders a collapsible control panel whose items map to layer visibility groups on the map. When the user toggles an item, the corresponding layers show or hide.</p>

<h2 id="definition">// definition</h2>
<p>Build a <code>MapLegendDefinition</code> to describe the legend structure. Each section contains items with an id, label, optional description, and a list of layer IDs to control.</p>

<CodeBlock Language="csharp" Files="@(new Dictionary<string, string>
{
    ["Legend definition"] =
@"var legend = new MapLegendDefinition(
    title: ""Map layers"",
    sections:
    [
        new MapLegendSection(""Infrastructure"",
        [
            new MapLegendItem(
                id: ""stations"",
                label: ""Stations"",
                description: ""Railway stations"",
                layerIds: [""stations-circle"", ""stations-label""]),
            new MapLegendItem(
                id: ""tracks"",
                label: ""Tracks"",
                layerIds: [""tracks-line""]),
        ]),
    ]);",
})" />

<h2 id="control_options">// control_options</h2>
<p><code>LegendControlOptions</code> sets the position and collapsed state of the legend panel on the map.</p>

<CodeBlock Language="csharp" Files="@(new Dictionary<string, string>
{
    ["Control options"] =
@"var options = new LegendControlOptions(
    Position: MapControlPosition.TopRight,
    Collapsed: false);",
})" />

<h2 id="custom_templates">// custom_templates</h2>
<p>Use the <code>ItemTemplate</code> render fragment to fully customize how each legend item appears. The template context provides the item definition, current visibility state, and a callback to toggle visibility.</p>

<p>See the <a href="components/tracked-data-source">TrackedDataSource train tracking example</a> for a full implementation with custom SVG swatch artwork and checkbox badges.</p>
